<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Statute lims:pit-date="2002-12-31" lims:lastAmendedDate="2002-12-31" lims:current-date="2025-07-24" lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80474" lims:id="80474" bill-origin="commons" bill-type="govt-public" xml:lang="en" in-force="yes" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80475" lims:id="80475"><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80476" lims:id="80476">An Act respecting a national child day</LongTitle><ShortTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80477" lims:id="80477" status="official">Child Day Act</ShortTitle><RunningHead lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80478" lims:id="80478">Child Day</RunningHead><BillHistory lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80479" lims:id="80479"><Stages lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80480" lims:id="80480" stage="assented-to"><Date><YYYY>1993</YYYY><MM>5</MM><DD>6</DD></Date></Stages><Stages lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" stage="consolidation"><Date><YYYY>2025</YYYY><MM>7</MM><DD>25</DD></Date></Stages></BillHistory><Chapter lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80482" lims:id="80482"><ConsolidatedNumber official="no">C-27.7</ConsolidatedNumber><AnnualStatuteId revised-statute="no"><AnnualStatuteNumber>18</AnnualStatuteNumber><YYYY>1993</YYYY></AnnualStatuteId></Chapter></Identification><Introduction lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80483" lims:id="80483"><Preamble lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80484" lims:id="80484" salutation="no"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80485" lims:id="80485" language-align="no" format-ref="indent-0-0" list-item="no"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80486" lims:id="80486">Preamble</MarginalNote><Text>WHEREAS on November 20, 1989, the Convention on the Rights of the Child was adopted in the United Nations General Assembly;</Text></Provision><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80487" lims:id="80487" language-align="no" format-ref="indent-0-0" list-item="no"><Text>AND WHEREAS the United Nations Convention on the Rights of the Child has been ratified by Canada;</Text></Provision><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80488" lims:id="80488" language-align="no" format-ref="indent-0-0" list-item="no"><Text>AND WHEREAS it is desirable to promote in Canada an awareness of the United Nations Convention on the Rights of the Child;</Text></Provision></Preamble><Enacts lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80489" lims:id="80489"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80490" lims:id="80490" language-align="no" format-ref="indent-0-0" list-item="no"><Text>NOW, THEREFORE, Her Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate and House of Commons of Canada, enacts as follows:</Text></Provision></Enacts></Introduction><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80491" lims:id="80491"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80492" lims:id="80492" level="1"><TitleText>Short Title</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:lastAmendedDate="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80493" lims:id="80493"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80494" lims:id="80494">Short title</MarginalNote><Label>1</Label><Text>This Act may be cited as the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="C-27.7">Child Day Act</XRefExternal>.</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80495" lims:id="80495" level="1"><TitleText>Child Day</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:lastAmendedDate="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80496" lims:id="80496"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2002-12-31" lims:fid="80497" lims:id="80497">Child day</MarginalNote><Label>2</Label><Text>Throughout Canada, in each and every year, the 20th day of November, being the day in the year 1989 when the United Nations Convention on the Rights of the Child was adopted in the United Nations General Assembly, shall be known as "Child Day".</Text></Section></Body></Statute>